sources.title: Executor | Full Movie | Action Crime Drama | Paul Sorvino
sources.description:
Executor - Kyle was raised by a corrupt priest who trained him to murder under the guise of executing God's justice. But when a hit-gone-wrong leaves a young boy orphaned, Kyle reluctantly takes the boy in. With the help of his beautiful neighbor, Kyle begins to re-evaluate his life's purpose and question the priest's twisted logic. 
2017.  Stars: Markiss McFadden, Paul Sorvino, Mischa Barton

metadata.Plot: Ruthless Assassin Kyle was raised by a corrupt priest who trained him to murder under the guise of executing God's justice. But when a hit-gone-wrong leaves a young boy orphaned, Kyle reluctantly takes the boy in. With the help of his beautiful neighbor, Kyle begins to re-evaluate his life's purpose and question the priest's twisted logic. However, the priest refuses to let go of his best soldier. Now, this ruthless assassin will have to fight to save the lives of his new found-family from his own mentor's vengeance.
metadata.Actors: Markiss McFadden, Paul Sorvino, Mischa Barton
